%% seq_05_org_membership_overview.mmd
%% Scope: Organization membership operations overview.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_05_org_invite.mmd
%%   - seq_05b_org_update_member_role.mmd
%%   - seq_05c_org_remove_member.mmd
%%   - seq_10_org_join_request.mmd

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor O as Org Owner/Admin
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Browser
    participant C as Controllers
    participant Cmd as Commands

    Note over O,Cmd: INVITE / ROLE / REMOVE FLOWS
    O->>UI: Execute membership administration actions
    UI->>C: /organization/* membership routes
    C->>Cmd: Invite, update role, remove member
    C-->>UI: Success/error state

    Note over U,Cmd: JOIN REQUEST FLOW
    U->>UI: Submit join request
    UI->>C: /organizations/:slug/join
    C->>Cmd: Create/process join request
    C-->>UI: Pending/approved/rejected state
